To miss electronic networks and constant connections in the world is not so bad.
On this day, I suddenly had to spend five hours at the airport because our plane had mechanical problems and had been replaced by another aircraft we had been waiting for.
So I had enough time to think about the nature of boredom.
I'm not gonna lie to you.
